BUILDING BLEXISMA-PROJECT
=========================

SETTING UP THE BUILD ENVIRONMENT
--------------------------------

Install maven (http://maven.apache.org)
    Developers did use Apache Maven 2.2.1...
Download and expand cougaar multi-agent plateform (http://www.cougaar.org/)
    expand cougaar.zip and cougaar-support.zip in your "$cougaar_install" folder.


DEFINING BUILDTIME AND RUNTIME PROPERTIES
------------------------------------------

??? configure maven personnal settings so that it defines each necessary properties.

